#   * R692 Squeak Smalltalk (TruffleSqueak) — 105th
#   * R696 Wren — 106th
#   * R700 Terra — 107th
#   * R704 Curv — 108th
#   * R708 Hoon (Urbit) — 109th
#   * R712 Newspeak (SOMns) — 110th (Bracha lineage)
#   * R716 Wenyan — 111th
